@node instal "Install rmw"

	To Install RMW you only need to copy one of the executables to c:
	and read the doc(this file)

	@{" Back to main " link main}
@endnode

@node useit "Using rmw"

	Starting rmw is simple, just start it with 'run rmw' or from wb,
	by double clicking on it's symbole. After a short loading, there it is
	in all it's glory. The rmw window :) Quiting the program isn't too
	hard either, it's just quite unusual. As you will find, the programs 
	window has no quit button and there's no menu's either, so how do u 
	quit, well, first you have to find out which process the program 
	is, then just break it with the command 'break <process>'.

	I know it's a unusual way, but I'll implent a menu in the program soon..
	
	@{" Back to main " link main}
@endnode

