@node intro "Information about what it is..  "


	DISCLAIMER:

	I will take no responsibilty whatsoever this orogram would cause!

	What is RMW, well it's just another memory displayer, I made it because 
	I didn't got one myself, of course it isn't so advanced, but I think it's
	alright. The strange name, comes from that in the beginning it showed
	all memory changes, everey change even if only a byte dissaoered it would
	show it, but the disadvantage was the speed, this version is 99 percent
	faster than the first version.
	
	Well that's what I wanted to say, so. . hope u like it. if not.. don't

	Don't forget, this is mail-ware so if u try it, send me an e-mail.

	@{" Back to main " link main}

@endnode
